    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "shifted perception? i dont know... it felt way more specific than that. like the guy was literally a duplicate. and it's not just that, i've been noticing these other things too. small things. like patterns repeating in the way people walk or even the weather acting weirdly predictable. it feels like the system is running low on assets or something. do u think it's possible that what we perceive as reality is actually just a simulation hitting some kind of resource limit?",
